What do I need for the counting game?

Variables:

--> Number we are currently on
--> People Playing the game --> array?
--> Who is saying the current number --> array of 2-value arrays?
--> Direction of the count (+/-)


Conditions:

--> If number is divisible by 7, direction changes 
	- until the next number that is divisble by 7
--> If number is divisible by 11, skip next player
	- continue counting in the same direction

What do we need to do?

--> start counting from 0
--> increment the number by 1
--> track who is saying what number
	- make a new array by adding both the count and the player saying the number?

def counting_game(input_number)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	players = ["one","two", "three", "four", "five", "six", "seven", "eight", "nine", "ten"]

	count = 0

	direction = 1
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	while the count is less than or equal to input_number
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		if count is equal to input_number
			
			print player[index] we are currently on

			break
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		if count is divisible by 7 

			direction = -1 until next time count is divisible by 7
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		if count is divisible by 11 

			direction = direction * 2
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		if (player[9] is reached) AND (direction = 1)

			go back to player[0]
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		if (player[0] is reached) AND (direction = -1)

			go to player[9]
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	increment the index by direction

	increment count += 1





